oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Home of Jim Newt Wills in Silver Lake Community
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Black and white photograph of the home of Jim Newt Wills located in Silver Lake Community. The image shows a horse in a fenced-in front yard.
The bricks were handmade and burned at the farm. Still standing and in excellent condition.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:source: Looking Back at Tennessee Photograph Collection, 1890-1981
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Horses; Fences; Yards; Houses
